<main class="px-1">

    <div class="text-center text-light" style="margin-top: 180px; padding: 0 15px;">
        <h1 style="font-size: clamp(50px, 6vw, 60px); text-align: center;">
            <div id="typewriter" class="typewriter-wrapper" style="word-break: break-word;">
                <span id="line1" class="typewriter-line1"></span><br/>
                <span id="line2" class="typewriter-line2"></span>
            </div>
        </h1>

        <p class="ease" style="font-size: clamp(20px, 4.5vw, 30px); margin-top: 30px; word-break: break-word;">
            Respondé, aprendé y ganá... <br/>¡La competencia recién empieza!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-light" style="margin-top: 140px; padding: 0 15px;">
        <p style="font-size: clamp(18px, 3.5vw, 21px); margin-bottom: 20px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; word-break: break-word;">
            ¿No tenés cuenta?
        </p>
        <a href="/POC/registro/show" class="registro" style="font-size: clamp(18px, 3.5vw, 21px);">Regístrate</a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-light fade-slide-up" style="margin-top: 130px; padding: 0 15px;">
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(35px, 6vw, 55px); font-weight: bold; word-break: break-word;">
            Ya estás adentro, ¿no?
        </h2>
        <p style="font-size: clamp(24px, 5vw, 35px); word-break: break-word;">
            Entonces no te achiques… <br/>
            ¡Seguí jugando!
        </p>
    </div>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-5" style="padding: 0 15px;">
        <div id="login-card"
             class="flex-row justify-content-center align-items-center"
             style="
            background-color: #010a7e;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: solid #dcb2fa 4px;
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 120px;
         "
        >
            <h3 class="text-center" style="color: #dcb2fa; font-size: clamp(26px, 4.5vw, 35px); word-break: break-word;">
                Iniciar Sesión
            </h3>
            <hr
                    style="
          margin-top: 0;
          border-top: 3px solid #dcb2fa;
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 410px;
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
        "
            />

            {{#error}}
                <div style="color: #ff6666; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px; text-align: center; word-break: break-word;">
                    {{error}}
                </div>
            {{/error}}

            <form action="/POC/login/validar" method="post"
                  style="margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 100%;">
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <label
                            for="email"
                            class="text-light"
                            style="margin-left: 10px; font-size: clamp(14px, 4vw, 18px); word-break: break-word;"
                    >Email</label>
                    <input
                            class="form-control"
                            style="border-radius: 30px;"
                            type="email"
                            name="email"
                            id="email"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                    <label
                            for="pass"
                            class="text-light"
                            style="margin-left: 10px; font-size: clamp(14px, 4vw, 18px); word-break: break-word;"
                    >Contraseña</label>
                    <input
                            class="form-control"
                            style="border-radius: 30px;"
                            type="password"
                            name="contrasena"
                            id="pass"
                    />
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4 d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <input
                            type="submit"
                            style="
              margin-top: 10px;
              background-color: #87ff5f;
              border: solid #cbffba 3px;
              text-decoration: none;
              color: #010a7e;
              padding: 5px;
              border-radius: 30px;
              padding-left: 50px;
              padding-right: 50px;
              font-size: clamp(16px, 4.5vw, 20px);
            "
                            value="Ingresar"
                    />
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

</main>

<div id="message-data" data-error="{{error}}" data-success="{{success}}" style="display:none;"></div>

<div id="popup-overlay">
    <div id="popup">
        <div id="popup-content">
            <span id="popup-message"></span>
            <button class="btn btn-lg boton-verde"
                    onclick="document.getElementById('popup-overlay').style.display='none'">Cerrar
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<script src="/POC/public/js/home.js"></script>

<!-- Div oculto para pasar mensajes desde Mustache a JS -->

<script>

    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    if (window.location.pathname !== '/POC') {
        window.history.replaceState(null, "", "/POC");
    }
});


</script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
